const Cart = (props) => (

    <path
      stroke="#14181F"

      d="M6.667 3 4 6.6v12.6c0 .477.187.935.52 1.273.334.337.786.527 1.258.527h12.444c.472 0 .924-.19 1.257-.527.334-.338.521-.796.521-1.273V6.6L17.333 3H6.667ZM4 7h16"
    />

      d="M16 11a4 4 0 1 1-8 0"

)

export default Cart
